column5: The Hamilton Bassmasters would like to welcome Mike Desforges to our next chapter meeting.  Date: Tuesday, February 8 Time: 7:00pm - 9:00pm  Location: Club G (865 Upper James Street, Hamilton) - at Mohawk/Upper James Intersection, in plaza behind Wendy's  Mike will be participating in a Question and Answer session with those in attendance. Mike has promised to hold nothing back!  Here is a link to Mike's website: http://mikedesforges.com/  If you have any questions email: [email protected], [email protected]
So, Mike can you give me a copy of all your waypoints for smallmouth... you promised to hold nothing back!..LOL wish I could be there to ask that question...LOL
lol someone will ask!! haha, they always do!
